{"tid":884541,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打返工返到有抑鬱或者懷疑自己有抑鬱","createTime":"2018-10-31T16:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T04:43:43.000Z","uid":137960,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68a30d76dd2a18e7a227929c4e89c90d3cef891c","tid":884541,"uid":137960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:27:58.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打返工返到有少少抑鬱既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家自己讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  見唔少巴打都係度呻工作煩惱  自己都有少少擔心。<br />\n如果大家有啲咩煩惱都可以擺係度發洩又好咩都好 甚至可以屌下我老母。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有需要不妨搵下我傾訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為小弟想做一個關於接近可能抑鬱打工仔既訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef9e920dbd8f6c0b68cd55208c549c235a9a151","tid":884541,"uid":137960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:28:33.000Z","msg":"Tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/torres9999999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftorres9999999&d=iKnCVhzc%2BzzjKiEVI3UiRv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3f3725a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/torres9999999</a>"},{"pid":"6d7a279d8884ae0d3c532dd52814d1a056f08227","tid":884541,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:30:10.000Z","msg":"你係大學邊個CENTER定係FYP"},{"pid":"c985a5beaea4d2ff2ef2807b4620c9513dd55f07","tid":884541,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:31:56.000Z","msg":"抑鬱咗都成十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由中學抑鬱到打牛工，見唔到人生有咩轉機，過得一日得一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7a88b0c8cb204ef523847c6ddd8358a1cd2d74","tid":884541,"uid":147892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:29:44.000Z","msg":"有呀<br />\n細個聽老豆老母講<br />\n話睇新聞見到佢地自殺真係覺得好傻<br />\n但到大個左出左黎